'''約翰·法蘭西斯·達利'''（{{lang-en|John Francis Daley}}，{{bd|1985年|7月20日}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]男演員、導演、編劇和監製。他以在[[國家廣播公司|NBC]]電視劇《{{le|怪胎與宅男|Freaks and Geeks}}》（1999年至2000年）中飾演山姆·威爾及在[[福斯廣播公司|FOX]]電視劇《[[尋骨線索|尋骨線索]]》（2007年至2014年）中飾演{{le|蘭斯·史崔特|Lance Sweets}}一角而聞名，並因此入圍了2014年的PRISM獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tv.com/shows/bones/cast/ |title=John Francis Daley as Lance Sweets |last= |first= |date= |website=[[TV.com|TV.com]] |access-date=2016-05-20 |archive-date=2016-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526105158/http://www.tv.com/shows/bones/cast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，他也在Dayplayer樂隊中彈琴和擔任歌手<ref>{{Citation | contribution-url = https://www.myspace.com/dayplayer | title = My space | contribution = Dayplayer | accessdate = 2018-02-27 | archive-date = 2018-05-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180504221903/https://myspace.com/dayplayer | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。

==早期生活==
約翰·法蘭西斯·達利出生於[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]]{{le|威靈 (伊利諾州)|Wheeling, Illinois|威靈}}。他是演員R·F·達利（R.F. Daley）和鋼琴老師南希·達利（Nancy Daley）的兒子。他的父親是[[愛爾蘭天主教|愛爾蘭天主教]]{{le|愛爾蘭天主教徒|Irish Catholics|徒}}，他的母親則是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Interfaith Celebrities: a Former Geek, the Equestrian Author, and an Aboriginal Jewish Doctor|url=http://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/Interfaith_Celebrities_a_Former_Geek_the_Equestrian_Author_and_an_Aboriginal_Jewish_Doctor.shtml|quote=|publisher={{le|InterfaithFamily.com|InterfaithFamily.com}}|date=2011-07-05|accessdate=2012-03-15|archive-date=2012-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120512081835/http://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/Interfaith_Celebrities_a_Former_Geek_the_Equestrian_Author_and_an_Aboriginal_Jewish_Doctor.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=John Francis Daley|url=https://www.twitter.com/JohnFDaley/status/172483499796860928|quote=For Ash Wednesday, I have my Irish Catholic dad put the ash on my forehead, then I have my Jewish mother lick her thumb and wipe it off.|publisher=Twitter – @JohnFDaley|date=2012-02-23|accessdate=2012-03-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=John Francis Daley on co-writing tonight's episode of 'Bones' and sharing a scene with his dad for the first time. (Awww.)|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/04/14/john-francis-daley-bones/|quote=I have sympathy nerves for everyone. I think it's the half-Jew in me.|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2011-04-14|accessdate=2013-06-04|archive-date=2013-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130222055418/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/04/14/john-francis-daley-bones/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Talented Mr Daley|url=http://meinmyplace.com/post/27910126610/john-francis-daley-me-in-my-place|quote=Um my mom's Jewish and my dad's Irish. I am in fact the same mix as Harrison Ford, which I like to point out as often as possible when I go on dates.|publisher=meinmyplace.com|date=September 2012|accessdate=2012-03-15|archive-date=2012-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727043205/http://meinmyplace.com/post/27910126610/john-francis-daley-me-in-my-place|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他主要都在[[紐約州|紐約州]]{{le|尼亞克 (紐約州)|Nyack, New York|尼亞克}}成長，並曾就讀於尼亞克中學（Nyack Middle School）。

==個人生活==
2016年2月6日，達利與演員柯琳娜·金斯伯里（Corinne Kingsbury）結婚，金斯伯里是[[泰特·唐納文|泰特·唐納文]]的前妻<ref>{{cite web |url=http://frostsnow.com/john-francis-daley |title=John Francis Daley Biography |date=2017-07-04 |website=Frost Snow |access-date=2018-02-27 |archive-date=2018-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227153504/http://frostsnow.com/john-francis-daley |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

